call it whatever you want,

01:26:28.110 --> 01:26:31.290
for what do you have
to really consider,

01:26:31.290 --> 01:26:33.490
and if you have objections,

01:26:33.490 --> 01:26:37.550
how do you overcome those
objections, and realistically,

01:26:37.550 --> 01:26:40.240
most of the objections
can be overcame

01:26:40.240 --> 01:26:42.780
with just speaking
rationally and dealing

01:26:42.780 --> 01:26:44.550
with any problems,
if they come up.

01:26:44.550 --> 01:26:45.850
&gt;&gt; Unidentified Speaker: Okay.

